{"tid":1237701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首辦外示威者呼籲警員與盧偉聰割蓆及罷工","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:44:24.000Z","uid":66324,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae70e00496ea134e2e358d938f93b671bde7356","tid":1237701,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:25:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463482-20190617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463482-20190617.htm&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=96a85102\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463482-20190617.htm&h=48b78216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463482-20190617.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方在上星期三金鐘衝突，出動布袋彈、橡膠子彈及150枚催淚彈，警務處處長盧偉聰晚上見傳媒時表示，是由現場指揮官專業判斷，視乎當時受到的威脅，決定當日使用甚麼武器。在特首辦對出集結的示威者，呼籲警員與盧偉聰割蓆及罷工。<br />\n<br />\n警方封鎖添華道行車線，有十多輛警車停泊在封鎖範圍。盧偉聰召開記者會之後，有示威者開始鼓噪，高呼「罷工有理，一哥割蓆」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n示威者與警方一度對峙後，警民氣氛緩和，部分示威者坐下唱聖詩，揮動手機形成燈海，又呼籲警察登記做選民「踢走盧偉聰」，有警員微笑回應。<br />\n================================<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad732e24472db872a1e1febd575750bf86bac732","tid":1237701,"uid":34154,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"有警員微笑回應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63772aa75a618a1e987fcf5b917ebb178ce1af81","tid":1237701,"uid":26708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"有警員微笑回應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d95a7527eba2cd6bc04f2b357c102b94bce4282","tid":1237701,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ae70e00496ea134e2e